&lt;li&gt;Design and build out dev, staging, and on-demand (ephemeral) environments that mirror production and spin up on request.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Treat environment provisioning as a product: fast, reproducible, self-service.&lt;/li&gt;
